<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Interview Cancelled</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .header {
            background-color: #e74c3c;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
        }

        .details {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 15px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Interview Cancelled</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear <strong>
                    <%= candidateName %>
                </strong>,</p>
            <p>We regret to inform you that your interview for the position of <strong>
                    <%= jobTitle %>
                </strong>, originally scheduled for <strong>
                    <%= scheduledTime %>
                </strong>, has been <strong>cancelled</strong>.</p>

            <div class="details">
                <h3>Reason for Cancellation</h3>
                <p>
                    <%= reason %>
                </p>
            </div>

            <p>We apologize for any inconvenience this may cause. If the interview is to be rescheduled, our team will
                notify you promptly.</p>
            <p>Thank you for your understanding.<br>The RecruitWay Team</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply directly to this email.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>